22. Scanners

For scanner support there is the package SANE (Scanner Access Now Easy).
Information can be found at [http://www.mostang.com/sane/] here. It can be
downloaded from [ftp://ftp.mostang.com/pub/sane/] here. This is a universal
scanner interface. It comes complete with documentation and several frontends
and backends.

More information on handheld scanners can be found at [http://
www.willamowius.de/scanner.html] here

Many scanners also have their own, scanner specific, software packages which
include drivers.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

