25. Appendix A. S3 cards supported by XFree86 3.3.x.

+---------------------------------+---------+---------+---+-----------+
|CHIPSET                          |RAMDAC   |CLOCKCHIP|BPP|CARD       |
+---------------------------------+---------+---------+---+-----------+
|                                 |         |         |   |           |
+---------------------------------+---------+---------+---+-----------+
|801/805                          |AT&T     |         |16 |Actix GE 32|
|                                 |20C490   |         |   |/ 32+ 2Mb  |
+---------------------------------+---------+---------+---+-----------+
|                                 |         |         |   |Orchid     |
|                                 |         |         |   |Fahrenheit |
|                                 |         |         |   |1280(+)    |
+---------------------------------+---------+---------+---+-----------+
|801/805                          |AT&T     |ICD2061A |16 |STB        |
|                                 |20C490   |         |   |PowerGraph |
|                                 |         |         |   |X.24       |
+---------------------------------+---------+---------+---+-----------+
|801/805                          |         |         |   |Del S3 805 |
+---------------------------------+---------+---------+---+-----------+
|                                 |         |         |   |Miro       |
