-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
26.11. ATA/IDE card drives

These card drives are supported starting with kernel 1.3.72. Both Flash-ATA
cards and rotating-media cards are supported. The very old Western Digital
40MB drives are not supported, because they do not conform to the PCMCIA ATA
specifications.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

26.12. ATA/IDE Interface Cards

  * Archos Zip100 MiniDrive (ide_cs)
   
